text: Prefer buying stuff at this outlet then the family mart located close by. The service staff seems to be more enthusiastic and pro-active here thus, the cashiering was done very quickly and efficiently. Many items to choose from, even the cooked ones. Personally I liked their curry puff, cheap and tasty.
